<p>Careers in Science.&nbsp; Take a look at some of the wide range of jobs that an education or training in science can lead to:</p><p>Recently broadcast on BBC2`s Learning Zone, this series of science career videos gives a unique insight into&nbsp;the everyday lives of young scientists and engineers from more unusual backgrounds.&nbsp;</p><table width="100%"><tr><td class="table_top_spacer" valign="top" align="center" width="25%"><a title="<p>As a Biochemist Dr Birgit Liss investigates Parkinson`s disease with the use of genetics.&nbsp; A short science career video showing how Birgit became a budding young scientist in the field of Biochemistry.&nbsp; In this video we enter the laboratory and see Birgit at work.</p>" onmouseover="return escape('<p>As a Biochemist Dr Birgit Liss investigates Parkinson`s disease with the use of genetics.&nbsp; A short science career video showing how Birgit became a budding young scientist in the field of Biochemistry.&nbsp; In this video we enter the laboratory and see Birgit at work.</p>')" href="../programme/55"><img height="100"  src="../../images/series_system/Snapshotsbirgit150.jpg_100x100.jpeg" width="100" border="0" /></a></td><td class="table_top_spacer" valign="top" align="center" width="25%"><a title="<p>In this short science career video we she how Sara McGowan uses science and art to design modern buildings as she embarks on a career in science and engineering as a Building Services Engineer.</p>" onmouseover="return escape('<p>In this short science career video we she how Sara McGowan uses science and art to design modern buildings as she embarks on a career in science and engineering as a Building Services Engineer.</p>')" href="../programme/53"><img height="100"  src="../../images/series_system/snapshotsenglarge150.jpg_100x100.jpeg" width="100" border="0" /></a></td><td class="table_top_spacer" valign="top" align="center" width="25%"><a title="<p>In this short science career video James describes himself as working in